These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, pineapple, papaya, onion
1. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | spinach | pineapple | papaya | onion |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, 7up, almond-milk
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | hot-chocolate | almond-milk | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, video-games, hiking, writing
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | gardening | hiking | video-games | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, family, romance, scientific
1. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | family | time-travel | scientific | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, lacrosse, ice-hockey, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | snowboarding | ice-hockey | lacrosse | skateboarding |

