.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, cabbage, grapefruit, radish
1. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the person eating cabbage is between the person eating apple and the person eating radish##2
3. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
4. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | radish | cabbage | apple | grapefruit |

