1. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | goat | hedgehog | bird | fish |

