.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, disco, metal, d&b
1. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
2. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
4. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | metal | disco | funk | d&b |

 